text: Fran Čubranić (born 11 June 1997) is a Croatian professional water polo player.Regionalna vaterpolo liga-Fran Čubranić Riječanin najbolji mladi vaterpolski golman svijeta: 'Ovo je dobar uvod za ostvarenje snova' Čubranić najbolji golman SP He is currently playing for VK Primorje. He is 6 ft 3 in (1.90 m) tall and weighs 209 lb (95 kg). ==References== ==External links== Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Croatian water polo players
